'''Carruthers, Landsbottom and Og''' is a {{Wp|law firm}} that has been referred to in a number of issues of [[Postbag from the Hedge]]. The firm appears to represent a number of clients, including Pirate [[Smith]], [[Klarense]], and the [[Consortium of Extra-Planar Merchandise Transferral Specialists]] responsible for selling many [[dragon equipment|dragon weapons]]. The firm is referenced in issues 13,{{CitePostbag|issue=13|letter=Letter 2|author=Carruthers, Landsbottom and Og}} 17,{{CitePostbag|issue=17|letter=Letter 8|author=Klarense}} and 20.{{CitePostbag|issue=20|letter=Letter 2|author=Pirate Smith}} It has not been featured in-game, although there is already an NPC named [[Og]]; whether he is the Og of the law firm is not known. The firm's legal consultant in the weapons division is [[C. P. L-F. Carruthers, Esq (LLB)]].

